{"tid":18298,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[聚熱風蛋]支那全球最快純電動超級跑車 NextEV NIO EP9！","createTime":"2016-12-02T08:08:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-02T08:27:18.000Z","uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bd3d8247bef918a77c678e2a66d9cf84b110a28a","tid":18298,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:08:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/nio-ep9-front34.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fnio-ep9-front34.jpg&h=a8896e76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一聽 &ldquo;超級跑車&quot; 這四個字，直覺都會想是歐洲品牌，例如林寶堅尼及法拉利等。但是今次中國大陸終於可以吐氣揚眉了，因為一家名為 NextEV (蔚來) 的中國汽車生產商日前在英國倫敦發表的最新款 NIO EP9 電動跑車，而且更於德國 N&uuml;rburgring 的 Green Hell 賽道上成功造出 7 分 5.12 秒最快紀錄，並成為全球最快的純電動超級跑車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/nio-ep9-.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fnio-ep9-.jpg&h=5834e0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一聽 &ldquo;超級跑車&quot; 這四個字，直覺都會想是歐洲品牌，例如林寶堅尼及法拉利等。但是今次中國大陸終於可以吐氣揚眉了，因為一家名為 NextEV (蔚來) 的中國汽車生產商日前在英國倫敦發表的最新款 NIO EP9 電動跑車，而且更於德國 N&uuml;rburgring 的 Green Hell 賽道上成功造出 7 分 5.12 秒最快紀錄，並成為全球最快的純電動超級跑車。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/nio-ep9-side.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2Fnio-ep9-side.jpg&h=39e6753d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n至於價格方面為 120 萬美元 (約 HK$931萬、NT$3,820萬)，初期更只限量生產 6 部。(編按:有 120萬美元還買這個??)<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/NextEV-Nio-EP9-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F11%2FNextEV-Nio-EP9-1.jpg&h=3a2448ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而開發這部世界最快純電動超級跑車的公司 NextEV 原來於 2014 年正式成立，只有兩年多歷史，但是背後實力容小覷，因為投資者包括騰訊 CEO 馬化騰及小米 CEO 雷軍等。而他們更有自己的 Formula E 車隊，製作超級跑車也有一定的經驗。<br />\n<br />\n有指 NextEV 將於市場上先推出價格較高的高階電動車，之後才會考慮推出價格更易負擔的車種。"},{"pid":"71ddfce17291b2feb3cf5d13e22362586e1fdd03","tid":18298,"uid":25556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:09:04.000Z","msg":"性能方面，NIO EP9 設有 4 個高性能電動引擎及 4 個獨立變速箱，並提供 1MW 最大輸出功率及 1,390 匹馬力。加速性能方面，由 0 至 200kph 只需 7.1 秒，而 0 至 96.6kph 則為 2.7 秒，最高時速可達 313kph。每次充滿電只需 45 分鐘，便可以行駛長達 427km。"},{"pid":"d273d49a6d3742307638a93aa87b3d12683c67d8","tid":18298,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:11:04.000Z","msg":"😅讓你坐"},{"pid":"6397ed0cae151eadf6c70b6b681c33a8178622ab","tid":18298,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"電更係影做啦，麼打黎之痳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"734b92bf3f3a8abdd92652558a1f0ed73a0ad370","tid":18298,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:13:53.000Z","msg":"電更易做啦，麼打黎之痳，裝多十個麼打馬力仲大添<br />\n但係入面用電會爆喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a45c3c40a9c6208324a3b36c2b1101ddbe167ca1","tid":18298,"uid":31269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:27:18.000Z","msg":"讓領導先坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}